bibdata.title: IEEE Test Procedure for Radial Power Factor Tests on Insulating Tapes in Paper-Insulated Power Cable
IEEE Test Procedure for Radial Power Factor Tests on Insulating Tapes in Paper-Insulated Power Cable

organization.name: Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers

bibdata.abstract: A test procedure for determining the radial power factor of insulating tapes in power cable is presented. Three-terminal type electrodes are mounted in a test cell and pressure is applied to the insulating tapes.<<ETX>>

organization.name: Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers
